    "user_title": "Create and edit PowerPoint presentations",
    "value_statement": "Creating and editing PowerPoint presentations is time-consuming and error-prone. This skill provides automated tools for converting HTML to PowerPoint, duplicating and reordering template slides, extracting text inventories for analysis, and validating XML structure.",
